/* ============================================================
 * AgentM Textual TUI вҖ” Claude-Code-style minimal chrome.
 *   в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
 *   в”Ӯ #status-header   (dock: top, h: 1, dim)  в”Ӯ   model В· turn В· tokens В· cost В· phase
 *   в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
 *   в”Ӯ #conversation-log (1fr)                   в”Ӯ   plain text flow
 *   в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
 *   в”Ӯ #input-bar  (dock: bottom, h: auto)       в”Ӯ   PromptInput TextArea
 *   в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
 *
 * Design: hierarchy comes from SYMBOLS (`> `, `в—Ҹ`, `вҺҝ`) and COLOR,
 * never from borders or block backgrounds. The conversation reads
 * top-to-bottom like a chat log; widgets are visually invisible
 * except for their text content.
 *
 * Theming uses Textual's built-in theme system; do NOT hardcode
 * hex colors here вҖ” reference variables ($primary, $surface, etc.)
 * so theme changes flow through.
 * ============================================================ */

Screen {
    background: $surface;
}

/* === top status header === */

/* Single dim italic strip; no background bar so it visually
 * recedes against the chat content. */
#status-header {
    dock: top;
    height: 1;
    background: transparent;
    color: $text-muted;
    padding: 0 2;
    text-style: italic;
    overflow: hidden hidden;
}

/* === bottom region: input bar === */

#input-bar {
    dock: bottom;
    height: auto;
    padding: 0 1;
    background: transparent;
}

#prompt-input {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 3;
    max-height: 8;
    border: round $accent 50%;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0 1;
}

#prompt-input:focus {
    border: round $accent;
}

/* === conversation log === */

#conversation-log {
    height: 1fr;
    padding: 0 2;
    background: transparent;
    scrollbar-background: $surface;
    scrollbar-color: $primary 30%;
    scrollbar-color-hover: $primary 60%;
}

/* All turn-level blocks: spacing only, no chrome. ``height: auto``
 * is critical вҖ” Vertical's default 1fr would make every turn try
 * to fill the viewport, so successive turns overlap and the
 * scroll never overflows. */
.turn,
.user-turn,
.tool-call,
.subagent {
    margin: 0 0 1 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    background: transparent;
}

/* === user turn вҖ” `> {text}` blockquote, no chrome === */

.user-turn {
    color: $text-muted;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Injected user message (api.send_user_message) вҖ” warning color
 * so the user can tell at a glance that this turn was synthesized
 * by an extension rather than typed. */
.user-turn.injected {
    color: $warning;
}

/* === assistant turn вҖ” plain markdown, no label === */

.turn {
    padding: 0;
}

/* Legacy ``в—Ҹ assistant`` label is no longer composed; the rule is
 * retained but hidden so any external CSS-targeting test still
 * resolves the class without producing a visible widget. */
.assistant-label {
    display: none;
}

/* === thinking block вҖ” italic dim, inline === */

.thinking {
    color: $text-muted;
    text-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 1 0;
    padding: 0;
    height: auto;
}

/* === tool call вҖ” `в–ј name(args)  вң“ Nms` title, indented body === */

.tool-call {
    padding: 0;
}

.tool-call > CollapsibleTitle {
    color: $accent;
    background: transparent;
    text-style: none;
}

.tool-call.failed > CollapsibleTitle {
    color: $error;
}

.tool-call:focus-within > CollapsibleTitle {
    text-style: bold;
}

/* Body indented by 4 spaces so the `вҺҝ  ` connector + content sit
 * under the title text the way Claude Code renders tool output. */
.tool-body {
    color: $text;
    padding: 0 0 0 4;
}

/* === subagent block вҖ” `в—Ҹ subagent(purpose)` + вҺҝ indented body === */

.subagent {
    padding: 0;
    layout: vertical;
}

.subagent-title {
    color: $accent;
    text-style: none;
}

.subagent.failed .subagent-title {
    color: $error;
}

.subagent-body {
    color: $text;
    padding: 0 0 0 4;
}

/* === modal screens вҖ” keep enough chrome to read against the
 * otherwise borderless main view === */

#command-palette,
#help-screen,
#info-modal {
    width: 90;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 80%;
    border: round $accent;
    padding: 1;
    background: $surface;
}

#command-palette OptionList {
    height: auto;
    max-height: 20;
}

#help-screen Static {
    width: 100%;
}

#info-modal {
    layout: vertical;
}

#info-modal .info-title {
    color: $accent;
    margin: 0 0 1 0;
}

#info-modal .info-body {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
}
